# Used automatically by `npm run build` (overrides .env for production builds).
# Relative /api keeps requests on the Netlify origin (HTTPS); the _redirects
# file in public/ proxies them to the backend. Fixes the mixed-content block.
#
# IF BACKEND MOVES TO RENDER: replace with your Render URL (must end in /api):
# VITE_API_URL=https://YOUR-APP-NAME.onrender.com/api
VITE_API_URL=/api
